WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.472 align:middle line:90%
[AUDIO LOGO]

00:00:03.472 --> 00:00:10.635 align:middle line:90%


00:00:10.635 --> 00:00:12.260 align:middle line:84%
>>MICHAEL LICHENS:
Best way to describe

00:00:12.260 --> 00:00:15.440 align:middle line:84%
the angelic realm is
they are ones that exist

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:17.690 align:middle line:90%
outside of time and space.

00:00:17.690 --> 00:00:19.880 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE NOORY: Are they
testing us for some reason?

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:20.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: They are.

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:23.960 align:middle line:84%
Especially, Saint Paul has
this reminder to everyone

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:26.180 align:middle line:84%
to entertain strangers
because sometimes people

00:00:26.180 --> 00:00:28.025 align:middle line:90%
entertain angels unaware.

00:00:28.025 --> 00:00:29.900 align:middle line:84%
One of the great things
about guardian angels

00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:31.350 align:middle line:90%
is it shows we're not alone.

00:00:31.350 --> 00:00:34.520 align:middle line:84%
We're not just left
here to exist and die.

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:36.080 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What's an archangel?

00:00:36.080 --> 00:00:39.440 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: They oversee
specifically God's realm

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:40.520 align:middle line:90%
and protect it.

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:42.650 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people, when
they encounter angels,

00:00:42.650 --> 00:00:45.170 align:middle line:84%
especially when the angels
appear in their full glory,

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:47.690 align:middle line:90%
are immediately afraid.

00:00:47.690 --> 00:00:49.730 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do they have
messages for us, Michael?

00:00:49.730 --> 00:00:50.543 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: They do.

00:00:50.543 --> 00:00:51.710 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What might they be?

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:52.918 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Of course, repent.

00:00:52.918 --> 00:00:56.780 align:middle line:84%
Flee from your sins,
but also return to God.

00:00:56.780 --> 00:00:59.402 align:middle line:90%
They're asking you to come back.

00:00:59.402 --> 00:01:03.333 align:middle line:90%
>>[BACKGROUND MUSIC]

00:01:03.333 --> 00:01:04.750 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Welcome
to Beyond Belief.

00:01:04.750 --> 00:01:08.860 align:middle line:10%
Michael J. Lichens with us, a
mysticism researcher with an MA

00:01:08.860 --> 00:01:12.370 align:middle line:10%
degree from the University
of Chicago Divinity School.

00:01:12.370 --> 00:01:16.420 align:middle line:84%
Michael's work focuses on
the very overlooked aspects

00:01:16.420 --> 00:01:17.710 align:middle line:90%
of spiritual life.

00:01:17.710 --> 00:01:19.580 align:middle line:84%
Michael, welcome
back to the program.

00:01:19.580 --> 00:01:21.520 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: Thank you so much
for having me again, George.

00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:23.840 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You did a great job
on Coast to Coast for us,

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:24.050 align:middle line:90%
by the way.

00:01:24.050 --> 00:01:24.925 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Thank you.

00:01:24.925 --> 00:01:26.860 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I'm still getting
emails from people.

00:01:26.860 --> 00:01:28.820 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: Being on that show
was like a dream come true.

00:01:28.820 --> 00:01:31.390 align:middle line:10%
I was one of those nerdy kids
who loved Art Bell, growing up.

00:01:31.390 --> 00:01:34.120 align:middle line:10%
And when you took over-- so
it's been a dream come true.

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:35.230 align:middle line:90%
I'm glad it went well.

00:01:35.230 --> 00:01:36.670 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How did
you get involved

00:01:36.670 --> 00:01:39.010 align:middle line:90%
in the aspect of mysticism?

00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:40.900 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: I got involved--

00:01:40.900 --> 00:01:42.430 align:middle line:84%
pretty much from
an early age, I was

00:01:42.430 --> 00:01:44.380 align:middle line:84%
raised in an
evangelical household

00:01:44.380 --> 00:01:46.060 align:middle line:90%
with a very Irish Catholic--

00:01:46.060 --> 00:01:47.605 align:middle line:90%
American Irish Catholic grandma.

00:01:47.605 --> 00:01:48.040 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Strict?

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:48.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Yes.

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.770 align:middle line:84%
So she would take me
to mass all the time.

00:01:50.770 --> 00:01:53.680 align:middle line:84%
And I loved-- I adored
her, so I, of course,

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.690 align:middle line:84%
wanted to learn about
her spirituality.

00:01:55.690 --> 00:01:58.960 align:middle line:84%
And that whole side of the
family, one of her daughters,

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:02.300 align:middle line:84%
my aunt, has psychic powers
and things of that nature.

00:02:02.300 --> 00:02:04.600 align:middle line:10%
So almost immediately,
from the time

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:06.010 align:middle line:10%
I could talk and
ask questions, I

00:02:06.010 --> 00:02:08.120 align:middle line:10%
wanted to know more about that.

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:11.260 align:middle line:10%
And then my career in
academia and editing

00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:13.950 align:middle line:10%
just kept going
in that direction.

00:02:13.950 --> 00:02:18.080 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now one of the great
aspects of mysticism is angels.

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:18.880 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Yes.

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:22.990 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And the angelic
realm is fascinating.

00:02:22.990 --> 00:02:25.208 align:middle line:90%
What is it?

00:02:25.208 --> 00:02:27.250 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: Best way to
describe the angelic realm

00:02:27.250 --> 00:02:32.080 align:middle line:84%
is they're still creatures much
like us, created by a creator,

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:36.260 align:middle line:84%
but they are ones that exist
outside of time and space.

00:02:36.260 --> 00:02:40.660 align:middle line:84%
So they're not bound like we are
by the laws of physics or time

00:02:40.660 --> 00:02:42.320 align:middle line:90%
or things of that nature.

00:02:42.320 --> 00:02:45.250 align:middle line:84%
But they exist in this
eternal communion with God.

00:02:45.250 --> 00:02:46.690 align:middle line:84%
Unless they're
the fallen angels,

00:02:46.690 --> 00:02:49.960 align:middle line:84%
that they exist in eternal
communion outside of God.

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:53.050 align:middle line:84%
And that is where they
exist for all of eternity,

00:02:53.050 --> 00:02:55.300 align:middle line:84%
having no place in
physics or time.

00:02:55.300 --> 00:02:57.730 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Why did they
fall, some of them?

00:02:57.730 --> 00:03:00.100 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: Some of them fell,
according to scriptures,

00:03:00.100 --> 00:03:02.748 align:middle line:84%
because Lucifer became
jealous of us humans.

00:03:02.748 --> 00:03:03.790 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: He was an angel.

00:03:03.790 --> 00:03:05.623 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: He was one
of the highest angels.

00:03:05.623 --> 00:03:07.900 align:middle line:90%
And his very name means light.

00:03:07.900 --> 00:03:10.780 align:middle line:84%
And he was thought to be one
of the more beautiful ones.

00:03:10.780 --> 00:03:14.020 align:middle line:84%
He after-- according
to scripture,

00:03:14.020 --> 00:03:15.610 align:middle line:84%
after humans were
created and we were

00:03:15.610 --> 00:03:18.580 align:middle line:84%
endowed with a physical soul
and creating God's image,

00:03:18.580 --> 00:03:20.530 align:middle line:90%
jealousy overtook him.

00:03:20.530 --> 00:03:22.600 align:middle line:84%
And he and one-third
of the angels

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:25.930 align:middle line:84%
rebelled against God before
being cast into hell.

00:03:25.930 --> 00:03:27.940 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now,
because it was God,

00:03:27.940 --> 00:03:31.660 align:middle line:84%
I have this feeling that
he allowed this to happen.

00:03:31.660 --> 00:03:33.160 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: He allowed
them to happen

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:36.850 align:middle line:84%
because one of the
great constants of God

00:03:36.850 --> 00:03:39.010 align:middle line:84%
in most Western religions
is that he allows

00:03:39.010 --> 00:03:41.080 align:middle line:90%
our free will to go about.

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:42.910 align:middle line:90%
And even angels have free will.

00:03:42.910 --> 00:03:44.650 align:middle line:84%
It's different from
us because once they

00:03:44.650 --> 00:03:47.710 align:middle line:84%
make a decision, due to
their eternal nature,

00:03:47.710 --> 00:03:49.750 align:middle line:90%
it's an eternal decision.

00:03:49.750 --> 00:03:52.700 align:middle line:90%
But he allowed it to happen.

00:03:52.700 --> 00:03:54.250 align:middle line:84%
And this also
allowed, say, Michael,

00:03:54.250 --> 00:03:55.810 align:middle line:84%
who we'll be
talking about today,

00:03:55.810 --> 00:03:59.020 align:middle line:84%
to show his warrior spirit
and cast Lucifer down

00:03:59.020 --> 00:04:00.190 align:middle line:90%
into the Earth.

00:04:00.190 --> 00:04:02.393 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Can we see
angels, Michael?

00:04:02.393 --> 00:04:04.810 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: If they want us to
see them, we absolutely can.

00:04:04.810 --> 00:04:06.940 align:middle line:84%
And they do often
show themselves to us.

00:04:06.940 --> 00:04:08.350 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: So they walk among us?

00:04:08.350 --> 00:04:10.270 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: They
can walk among us.

00:04:10.270 --> 00:04:12.400 align:middle line:84%
Scripture and
mystics have reported

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:15.160 align:middle line:84%
that they will sometimes
appear as just regular humans--

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:16.720 align:middle line:84%
the beggar, the
guy who's knocking

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:18.950 align:middle line:90%
on your door asking for food.

00:04:18.950 --> 00:04:20.140 align:middle line:90%
So they can appear human.

00:04:20.140 --> 00:04:22.840 align:middle line:84%
They can also sometimes
appear in their actual form,

00:04:22.840 --> 00:04:23.860 align:middle line:90%
which is terrifying.

00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:26.020 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Are they testing
us for some reason?

00:04:26.020 --> 00:04:26.950 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: They are.

00:04:26.950 --> 00:04:30.100 align:middle line:84%
Especially Saint Paul has
this reminder to everyone

00:04:30.100 --> 00:04:32.290 align:middle line:84%
to entertain strangers
because sometimes people

00:04:32.290 --> 00:04:34.120 align:middle line:90%
entertain angels unaware.

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:36.310 align:middle line:84%
And that's a calling to
the ancient Christian idea

00:04:36.310 --> 00:04:40.850 align:middle line:84%
of hospitality that we give
to people as much as we can.

00:04:40.850 --> 00:04:43.480 align:middle line:84%
And so we do that knowing
that they're strangers,

00:04:43.480 --> 00:04:45.100 align:middle line:84%
but they very well
might be angels.

00:04:45.100 --> 00:04:47.540 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: They say we're all
assigned a guardian angel.

00:04:47.540 --> 00:04:48.340 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Yes.

00:04:48.340 --> 00:04:49.090 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Is that true?

00:04:49.090 --> 00:04:50.798 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: We are all,
each and every one

00:04:50.798 --> 00:04:52.963 align:middle line:84%
of us, assigned a guardian
angel, absolutely.

00:04:52.963 --> 00:04:54.880 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now, does the
guardian angel have any

00:04:54.880 --> 00:04:55.870 align:middle line:90%
say so with the matter?

00:04:55.870 --> 00:04:58.870 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: [LAUGHS] I
don't know specifically

00:04:58.870 --> 00:05:01.623 align:middle line:84%
if it's like the job
posting, but they still

00:05:01.623 --> 00:05:03.790 align:middle line:84%
have their free will to do
the will of God, so yeah,

00:05:03.790 --> 00:05:05.880 align:middle line:90%
they do have the say in us.

00:05:05.880 --> 00:05:08.380 align:middle line:84%
But I don't know if they have
a say in each specific person.

00:05:08.380 --> 00:05:10.938 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do we each
have one guardian angel?

00:05:10.938 --> 00:05:12.730 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: We each have
one guardian angel,

00:05:12.730 --> 00:05:16.120 align:middle line:84%
but sometimes other angels
can take an interest in us.

00:05:16.120 --> 00:05:18.490 align:middle line:84%
In the Old Testament,
there was this story

00:05:18.490 --> 00:05:21.670 align:middle line:84%
of Tobit, who Raphael,
the archangel,

00:05:21.670 --> 00:05:25.487 align:middle line:84%
had befriended him while
disguised as a human.

00:05:25.487 --> 00:05:27.070 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Tell me
some stories that you

00:05:27.070 --> 00:05:30.740 align:middle line:84%
may have heard about people
dealing with their guardian

00:05:30.740 --> 00:05:31.540 align:middle line:90%
angels.

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:32.560 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Absolutely.

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:37.000 align:middle line:84%
So one of my absolute
favorites is Padre Pio, who--

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:39.242 align:middle line:84%
Christian mystic extraordinaire
of the 20th century.

00:05:39.242 --> 00:05:40.450 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: He had the stigmata.

00:05:40.450 --> 00:05:41.742 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: He had the stigmata.

00:05:41.742 --> 00:05:44.200 align:middle line:84%
He would also get the other
wounds of Christ on him.

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:45.160 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yes, exactly.

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:47.230 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: He would
frequently talk not just

00:05:47.230 --> 00:05:49.030 align:middle line:84%
to his own guardian
angel, he could

00:05:49.030 --> 00:05:52.480 align:middle line:84%
commune with other guardian
angels for other people.

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.670 align:middle line:84%
And whenever anyone asked
him for prayer requests,

00:05:54.670 --> 00:05:56.670 align:middle line:84%
he would often say just
tell your guardian angel

00:05:56.670 --> 00:05:57.610 align:middle line:90%
to tell mine.

00:05:57.610 --> 00:05:58.750 align:middle line:90%
And they will tell me.

00:05:58.750 --> 00:05:59.710 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And they'll
take care of it.

00:05:59.710 --> 00:06:00.510 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Yeah.

00:06:00.510 --> 00:06:03.670 align:middle line:84%
And this was proven to him
when a pilgrim was coming

00:06:03.670 --> 00:06:06.873 align:middle line:90%
to see him, and their bus had--

00:06:06.873 --> 00:06:08.290 align:middle line:84%
their breaks went
out on their bus

00:06:08.290 --> 00:06:09.195 align:middle line:90%
and they were in an accident.

00:06:09.195 --> 00:06:09.995 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, jeez.

00:06:09.995 --> 00:06:12.850 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: So this woman just
prayed to her guardian angel,

00:06:12.850 --> 00:06:15.820 align:middle line:84%
protect me and let Padre
Pio know that I'm coming,

00:06:15.820 --> 00:06:17.050 align:middle line:90%
but I need help.

00:06:17.050 --> 00:06:19.840 align:middle line:84%
And the moment she arrived,
a few minutes later,

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:21.470 align:middle line:84%
Padre Pio immediately
comes over to her

00:06:21.470 --> 00:06:23.050 align:middle line:84%
and says your guardian
angel came to me

00:06:23.050 --> 00:06:24.550 align:middle line:84%
and told me you
were needing prayer.

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:26.180 align:middle line:90%
Were you in an accident?

00:06:26.180 --> 00:06:28.900 align:middle line:84%
And this happened constantly
in the confessional,

00:06:28.900 --> 00:06:30.730 align:middle line:84%
where before people
could talk, he'd

00:06:30.730 --> 00:06:34.210 align:middle line:84%
say your angel already spoke
to me or something like that.

00:06:34.210 --> 00:06:36.640 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I had a call on Coast
to Coast several years ago

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:38.800 align:middle line:90%
during my open line section.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:41.860 align:middle line:84%
And the lady was telling me
about her guardian angel.

00:06:41.860 --> 00:06:44.920 align:middle line:84%
And she was in a
car with her husband

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:47.950 align:middle line:84%
and they were weaving
in and out of traffic,

00:06:47.950 --> 00:06:49.690 align:middle line:90%
and it was nighttime.

00:06:49.690 --> 00:06:52.720 align:middle line:84%
And they pulled to the
left to pass a truck.

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:58.300 align:middle line:84%
And as they did, guess what,
a car was coming right at them

00:06:58.300 --> 00:06:59.305 align:middle line:90%
from the other side--

00:06:59.305 --> 00:06:59.680 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Oh, my gosh.

00:06:59.680 --> 00:07:01.000 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: --right at them.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:03.430 align:middle line:84%
And she's praying, oh,
God, please, help me.

00:07:03.430 --> 00:07:05.320 align:middle line:90%
Oh, God please help me.

00:07:05.320 --> 00:07:09.220 align:middle line:84%
And I guess when you pray
to God, he sends the angels.

00:07:09.220 --> 00:07:13.240 align:middle line:84%
She said at that moment,
when she started praying,

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:19.630 align:middle line:84%
the two cars merged and went
through each other, almost like

00:07:19.630 --> 00:07:20.440 align:middle line:90%
ghosts.

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:21.580 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Oh, my.

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:24.190 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And one car
went the other way

00:07:24.190 --> 00:07:29.050 align:middle line:84%
and they went their way,
and nobody got hurt.

00:07:29.050 --> 00:07:30.635 align:middle line:90%
How does that happen?

00:07:30.635 --> 00:07:32.260 align:middle line:84%
>>LICHENS: Couldn't
tell you the exact,

00:07:32.260 --> 00:07:34.510 align:middle line:84%
but it's the miracles
they can work.

00:07:34.510 --> 00:07:37.040 align:middle line:84%
Again, they're not bound
by physics like we are.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:39.550 align:middle line:84%
They don't-- they can change
their appearance if they need

00:07:39.550 --> 00:07:40.350 align:middle line:90%
to.

00:07:40.350 --> 00:07:43.390 align:middle line:84%
They can move things
and move through time.

00:07:43.390 --> 00:07:46.510 align:middle line:84%
I've never heard of something
quite that extraordinary.

00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:47.720 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's amazing.

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:49.053 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Oh, the heart attack.

00:07:49.053 --> 00:07:50.560 align:middle line:90%
I am sure that when he--

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:52.977 align:middle line:84%
I bet that person never asks
when does God answer prayers.

00:07:52.977 --> 00:07:54.935 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Favorite movie,
"It's a Wonderful Life

00:07:54.935 --> 00:07:55.760 align:middle line:90%
with Jimmy Stewart"

00:07:55.760 --> 00:07:56.560 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: Yes.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:59.810 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And he was there,
ready to commit suicide.

00:07:59.810 --> 00:08:01.450 align:middle line:90%
He was so despondent.

00:08:01.450 --> 00:08:03.760 align:middle line:84%
And that's when they
sent the angel, Clarence,

00:08:03.760 --> 00:08:04.870 align:middle line:90%
down to save him.

00:08:04.870 --> 00:08:05.800 align:middle line:90%
And he did.

00:08:05.800 --> 00:08:06.640 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: He did.

00:08:06.640 --> 00:08:08.710 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So they get involved
in our life, don't they.

00:08:08.710 --> 00:08:09.250 align:middle line:90%
>>LICHENS: They did.

00:08:09.250 --> 00:08:11.710 align:middle line:84%
And what I loved about that
depiction of guardian angels,

00:08:11.710 --> 00:08:15.370 align:middle line:84%
he was responding not to just
Jimmy Stewart's character

00:08:15.370 --> 00:08:16.300 align:middle line:90%
but everyone.

00:08:16.300 --> 00:08:17.980 align:middle line:84%
The whole town was
praying for him

00:08:17.980 --> 00:08:20.120 align:middle line:84%
because they knew
he was in crisis.

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:22.210 align:middle line:84%
So, in a way,
Clarence was an answer

00:08:22.210 --> 00:08:24.280 align:middle line:84%
to a prayer hundreds
of people were

00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:26.987 align:middle line:84%
praying, and had no idea how
their prayer would be answered.

00:08:26.987 --> 00:08:27.820 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Absolutely.

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:30.250 align:middle line:84%
Well, angels communicate with
people in different ways.

00:08:30.250 --> 00:08:32.679 align:middle line:84%
On Gaia's "Open
Minds," Belinda Womack

00:08:32.679 --> 00:08:35.890 align:middle line:84%
describes a way to
contact the angelic realm.

00:08:35.890 --> 00:08:36.880 align:middle line:90%
Fascinating.

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:37.680 align:middle line:90%
[VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:41.929 align:middle line:10%
