our reality because we

00:08:58.690 --> 00:09:00.950 align:middle line:90%
are creating our lives.

00:09:00.950 --> 00:09:04.780 align:middle line:84%
And so if we say, I
surrender and help me,

00:09:04.780 --> 00:09:11.140 align:middle line:84%
that allows these awesome,
wonderful executive producers

00:09:11.140 --> 00:09:13.900 align:middle line:84%
to step in and to
help us to change

00:09:13.900 --> 00:09:17.350 align:middle line:84%
the movie we are dreaming,
