00:09:22.930 --> 00:09:26.830 align:middle line:84%
when I say, hey, I need
some help with this one.

00:09:26.830 --> 00:09:28.900 align:middle line:84%
Or even if I don't ask,
they know me well enough

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:30.190 align:middle line:90%
to know where I do.

00:09:30.190 --> 00:09:37.340 align:middle line:84%
And the degree of creativity
to which they solve problems

00:09:37.340 --> 00:09:39.050 align:middle line:84%
is mind-boggling
to me all the time.

00:09:39.050 --> 00:09:40.910 align:middle line:84%
It's like I could
have never come up

00:09:40.910 --> 00:09:42.200 align:middle line:90%
with that as a solution.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.640 align:middle line:90%
That is brilliant.

00:09:43.640 --> 00:09:49.170 align:middle line:84%
It's far beyond anything that
we would calculate on our own.

00:09:49.170 --> 00:09:53.000 align:middle line:84%
>> But at the same time, we're
not giving our power away.

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:55.100 align:middle line:10%
And they really make
this is important,

00:09:55.100 --> 00:09:59.870 align:middle line:10%
that they work through us,
through the concept of oneness,

00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:02.540 align:middle line:10%
which again is
challenging for the ego

00:10:02.540 --> 00:10:06.050 align:middle line:10%
to understand because the
ego thinks, hey, I'm it.

00:10:06.050 --> 00:10:07.714 align:middle line:90%
I'm me and you're you.

00:10:07.714 --> 00:10:10.560 align:middle line:84%
And you're over there
and I'm over here.

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:13.830 align:middle line:90%
But really, we are all one.

00:10:13.830 --> 00:10:15.590 align:middle line:90%
We are so connected.

00:10:15.590 --> 00:10:22.130 align:middle line:84%
And so when we just ask for
