00:10:22.130 --> 00:10:24.720 align:middle line:90%
whatever the problem is--

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:27.860 align:middle line:84%
and as you know,
the more we ask,

00:10:27.860 --> 00:10:32.360 align:middle line:84%
the easier it becomes
