her that she would give birth

00:16:28.140 --> 00:16:29.550 align:middle line:90%
to the son.

00:16:29.550 --> 00:16:34.457 align:middle line:84%
And that-- and he appears many
times in different connections.

00:16:34.457 --> 00:16:36.540 align:middle line:84%
He appeared, of course,
to the children of Fatima,

00:16:36.540 --> 00:16:38.760 align:middle line:84%
along with the
Archangel Michael.

00:16:38.760 --> 00:16:42.300 align:middle line:84%
And then many, many Irish
Saints, particularly off

00:16:42.300 --> 00:16:45.120 align:middle line:84%
