at Skellig Michael,

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:48.300 align:middle line:84%
many monks had
encountered the archangel

00:16:48.300 --> 00:16:50.525 align:middle line:84%
at that very space,
which is interesting

00:16:50.525 --> 00:16:52.650 align:middle line:84%
because there weren't a
lot of people in that area.

00:16:52.650 --> 00:16:56.100 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: There's a
religious song called "Ave"

00:16:56.100 --> 00:16:59.220 align:middle line:90%
