00:41:49.410 --> 00:41:52.680 align:middle line:84%
>> We are appreciative of the
opportunity to be of service

00:41:52.680 --> 00:41:53.760 align:middle line:90%
unto you.

00:41:53.760 --> 00:41:55.570 align:middle line:90%
