00:41:55.570 --> 00:42:00.510 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, Theo, we would like
to open it up for you to choose

00:42:00.510 --> 00:42:02.252 align:middle line:84%
who you wish to
speak to unless--

00:42:02.252 --> 00:42:03.960 align:middle line:84%
well, you know what,
first, why don't you

00:42:03.960 --> 00:42:06.600 align:middle line:84%
give us your perspective
on soul integration?

00:42:06.600 --> 00:42:09.300 align:middle line:84%
We just heard a little bit
from Marcus and Sheila on that.

00:42:09.300 --> 00:42:12.030 align:middle line:84%
And just introduce the
subject a bit to our viewers

00:42:12.030 --> 00:42:13.410 align:middle line:90%
before we go to the questions.

00:42:13.410 --> 00:42:16.020 align:middle line:84%
>> Soul integration is
coming into the wholeness

00:42:16.020 --> 00:42:20.610 align:middle line:84%
of your being, the recognition
of the divine essence that you

00:42:20.610 --> 00:42:22.920 align:middle line:90%
are, the master that you are.

00:42:22.920 --> 00:42:27.360 align:middle line:84%
This fifth dimensionary energy
is fully about the planet now.

00:42:27.360 --> 00:42:30.390 align:middle line:84%
Never before have
human beings been

00:42:30.390 --> 00:42:33.990 align:middle line:84%
available to recognize
their masterhood.

00:42:33.990 --> 00:42:38.670 align:middle line:84%
The fifth dimensionary energy
is a place of refined vibration

00:42:38.670 --> 00:42:41.970 align:middle line:84%
that allows each
individual to recognize

00:42:41.970 --> 00:42:46.320 align:middle line:84%
the divine essence,
the master, and express

00:42:46.320 --> 00:42:48.070 align:middle line:90%
that in their daily life.

00:42:48.070 --> 00:42:51.180 align:middle line:84%
The third dimension
being physical reality.

00:42:51.180 --> 00:42:53.580 align:middle line:84%
The fourth was the
spiritual awakening.

00:42:53.580 --> 00:42:58.860 align:middle line:84%
And now as science
speaks about as well

00:42:58.860 --> 00:43:02.680 align:middle line:84%
is the fifth-dimensional
waves if you would,

00:43:02.680 --> 00:43:06.430 align:middle line:84%
on a higher frequency
level of recognition.

00:43:06.430 --> 00:43:10.620 align:middle line:84%
So it is a release of
beliefs of old paradigms that

00:43:10.620 --> 00:43:16.500 align:middle line:84%
no longer work any longer, that
allows for this transmutation,

00:43:16.500 --> 00:43:21.090 align:middle line:84%
if you would, this homecoming
into the alignment of wholeness

00:43:21.090 --> 00:43:24.690 align:middle line:84%
or holiness, divinity
expressed fully,

00:43:24.690 --> 00:43:26.750 align:middle line:90%
unencumbered from the past.

